{"id":610976,"date":[{"year":1981,"month":3,"day":28}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"爱国名言","genre":"","count":"106","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱国名言","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"△以身许国，何事不可为?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——岳飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△身上征衣杂酒痕，远游无处不消魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此生合是忘家客，风雨登轮出国门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——何叔衡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△祖国陆沉人有责，天涯飘泊我无家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——秋瑾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△莽莽神州叹陆沉，救时——无计愧偷生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——秋瑾"}]}